  "Name": {
    "English": "STARBORN PHOENIX",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "星之子凤凰",
    "TraditionalChinese": "星辰之子鳳凰"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Starborn Phoenix",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "星之子凤凰",
    "TraditionalChinese": "星辰之子鳳凰"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Exclusive Spacecraft",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属飞船",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊太空船"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">reforged starship</span>, commemorating a time when Travellers old and new joined together to voyage across the stars.<br><br>This unusual ship is optimized for effortless gliding during flight, while a localized vector field allows the craft to hover above solid planes.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">重新打造的专属飞船</span>，为了纪念那段新老旅行者携手共进，一同探索群星的时光。<br><br>这艘不同寻常的飞船经过了优化改造，因此能够在飞行期间毫无阻力地顺畅滑行，除此以外一个局部范围的矢量场将允许飞船飘浮在实体平面之上。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">领取</span>这艘飞船并将其添加至你的收藏，或者与你的当前飞船进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，通过快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這艘獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">重鑄太空船</span>，紀念新老旅行者曾一同探索星辰的美好時光。<br><br>這艘特殊的太空船具備優化的飛行性能，能在空中平穩滑行，並借助局部向量場技術懸浮於地面上。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘太空船加入你的收藏，或是<span class=\"name name-stellar\">替換</span>目前的太空船。在星球上時，可利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
